Cynthia A. Pivacek
}}}
{\b0 \cf24 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
, J., granted restaurant and city\rquote s motion to dismiss. Landowner appealed.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf24 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
\par 
}
}
{\b0 \cf24 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
