{\b0 \cf24 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 landowner was not procedurally barred from seeking declaratory and injunctive relief although landowner had failed to seek certiorari review regarding resolution of city\rquote s design review board approving restaurant\rquote s plans to renovate building;
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf24 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
\par 
}
