{\b0 \cf24 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
Affected landowner was not procedurally barred from seeking declaratory and injunctive relief regarding city\rquote s decision to allow restaurant to operate in building without providing any off-street parking, although landowner had failed to seek certiorari review regarding resolution of city\rquote s design review board approving restaurant\rquote s plans to renovate building, where resolution did not mention parking, and city planning director\rquote s notation from several months after resolution was issued confirmed that parking credits had yet to be determined.
\par 
}
}
}
