{\b0 \cf24 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
\u8220\'3fRes judicata\u8221\'3f is a procedural bar that prohibits relitigation of claims in a subsequent cause of action and includes claims that were raised or could have been raised in the prior action.
\par 
