{\b0 \cf24 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
Separation of powers did not bar landowner\rquote s declaratory judgment action challenging city\rquote s award of parking credits to restaurant without engaging variance procedure; landowner was not requesting that city perform some discretionary act, but rather landowner alleged that city engaged in ultra vires act.
