{\super \b1 \cf37 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
[7]
}}}
{\b0 \cf24 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 Olde Naples and the City argue on appeal that the trial court\rquote s dismissal can be affirmed on the alternative basis of res judicata or collateral estoppel, thus making a tipsy coachman
}
{\b0 \cf24 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_B00012038189609_ID0EZJBG_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_B00012038189609_ID0EZJBG_1}
{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "#co_footnote_B00012038189609_1" }{\fldrslt 
