}
{\b0 \cf26 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 753 So.2d 114, 116 (Fla. 4th DCA 1999)
}}}
{\b0 \cf24 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
). The rule generally provides that a party must claim and recover in one action all damages sustained or accruing from one wrongful act. 
}
{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.westlaw.com/Link/Document/FullText?findType=Y&serNum=2034719556&pubNum=0003926&originatingDoc=I28b869c3c85411e5a795ac035416da91&refType=RP&fi=co_pp_sp_3926_1147&originationContext=document&vr=3.0&rs=cblt1.0&transitionType=DocumentItem&contextData=(sc.CustomDigest)#co_pp_sp_3926_1147" }{\fldrslt 
