{\b0 \cf26 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 at 870
}}}
{\b0 \cf24 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
. The Third District determined that the municipality\rquote s discretion to prosecute an enforcement action \u8220\'3fis a purely executive function that cannot be supervised by the courts, absent the violation of a specific constitutional provision or law.\u8221\'3f 
}
{\b0 \cf24 \f2 \i0 \fs20 
